title: Kingo Android Root 1.2.3.2051
description:
Kingo ROOT is a handy and efficient program designed to root Android devices in a one-click operation, safe and easy.Kingo ROOT automatatically recognizes your Android device, allowing you to perform a root operation with just a mouse click. Subsequently, you can remove the root just as simple.
